teamcardone.name: Omowumi Adekoya
teamcardone.text: In my spare time, I enjoy reading novels.

teamcardtwo.name: Damilola Obidiaro
teamcardtwo.text: I create time to intellectually debate with my family. I destress by listening to music or creating music with my voice and guitars. It gives me a lot of pleasure and satisfaction to garden and see my plants grow slowly and suddenly. In my spare time, I engage with thought-provoking books and epic/sci-fi movies.

teamcardthree.name: Titilayo Ekundayo
teamcardthree.text: From hosting my own podcast, The Abeg who send me podcast, to taking taekwondo courses, gardening, and being an active member of Toastmasters International, I enjoy trying new things. A good meal and intellectual discourse can win my heart anytime anyday.

teamcardfour.name: Aisha Adeleke
teamcardfour.text: I have always wanted to have a Tiger as a pet because I find the fur prints attractive and I also love cat families, but I got a cat because I can't have a tiger.

teamcardfive.name: Opeyemi Bioku
teamcardfive.text: Enjoying good music across many genres as well as movies in my leisure is my favorite thing to do.

teamcardsix.name: Adam Yakub
teamcardsix.text: As early as 6a.m, I’m always at the football pitch every Saturday.

teamcardseven.name: Seun Oladele
teamcardseven.text: Music is what I love to do. That’s the only fun thing I know. I play video games a lot and watch movies a lot. For someone considered a researcher, I do not really like reading.
